      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "は～、やっと戻って来れた～",
      "startTime": 3.6000001352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "午前中にレッスン、午後は月スト五人でインタビュー\nそれから次のライブの打ち合わせをして",
      "startTime": 12.6333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "最後は読書系動画配信者のチャンネルにゲスト出演……\n凄く濃い一日でしたね",
      "startTime": 21.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になってから、月ストだけじゃなくて\nメンバーそれぞれのソロの仕事も格段に増えたな",
      "startTime": 27.2000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛小説が好き……という話をあちこちでするように\nなってから、関係するお仕事が多くなった気がします",
      "startTime": 35.4333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "まさかお仕事に繋がるとは思ってなかったんですけど\n世界が広がった感じがしてとっても嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 44.6573858341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら良かったよ\n少しでも無理があったらいつでも言ってくれ",
      "startTime": 50.6333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "この後は、今度のお仕事についての軽い打ち合わせ\nですよね",
      "startTime": 58.0666650136,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}